---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Work | HALM Collective">
  <div class="container mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Work at HALM</h1>
    <p class="mb-6">Discover inspiring spaces designed for productivity, creativity, and collaboration.</p>
    
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p>HALM offers versatile workspaces that cater to different working styles and needs. Whether you prefer a quiet desk, a collaborative setting, or a change of scenery throughout your day, our spaces are designed to enhance your productivity and wellbeing.</p>
      
      <h2 class="mt-8">Workspace Options</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-4">
        <div class="card p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Hot Desks</h3>
          <p>Flexible workspaces available on a first-come, first-served basis. Perfect for members who visit occasionally or prefer variety in their work environment.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Dedicated Desks</h3>
          <p>Your personal workspace within our community. Includes lockable storage and the comfort of knowing your space is always waiting for you.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Private Offices</h3>
          <p>Enclosed spaces for teams of 1-6 people. All the benefits of the HALM community with the privacy your work requires.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="mt-8">Amenities</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-4">
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
          <div class="text-primary mt-1">✓</div>
          <div>High-speed fiber internet with secure WiFi</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
          <div class="text-primary mt-1">✓</div>
          <div>Printing, scanning, and copying services</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
          <div class="text-primary mt-1">✓</div>
          <div>Bookable meeting rooms with A/V equipment</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
          <div class="text-primary mt-1">✓</div>
          <div>Phone booths for private calls</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
          <div class="text-primary mt-1">✓</div>
          <div>Discounted cafe food and beverages</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
          <div class="text-primary mt-1">✓</div>
          <div>Access to wellness classes and events</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
          <div class="text-primary mt-1">✓</div>
          <div>24/7 access for dedicated members</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
          <div class="text-primary mt-1">✓</div>
          <div>Mail and package handling</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="mt-8">Membership Options</h2>
      <p>Our work memberships are designed to be flexible and accommodate different needs and budgets.</p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-4">
        <div class="card p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Day Pass</h3>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">$25/day</p>
          <p>Perfect for visitors or occasional users who need a productive space for the day.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Hot Desk Membership</h3>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">$199/month</p>
          <p>Unlimited access to any available hot desk during regular hours.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Dedicated Desk</h3>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">$349/month</p>
          <p>Your personal workspace available 24/7 with lockable storage.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="/community/memberships" class="bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-primary-dark transition">Explore Membership Options</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="ml-4 px-6 py-3 border border-primary text-primary rounded-md hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition">Schedule a Tour</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
